        "post-award",
        "other",
        "n/a"
      ],
      "filterTypes": [
        "policies"
      ],
      "tooltip": "Either 'Pre-award' or 'Post-award' is chosen when the policy makes clear that the DMP should be prepared at one of these stages. 'Other' is used for any other stage, together with further information in the notes field. 'Not applicable' is used when the policy addresses this poorly or not at all."
